@startuml Splash_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> Animating : startEntranceAnimation()
Animating --> Waiting : Animation Complete (3 seconds)

Waiting --> CheckingLogin : checkLoginStatusAndNavigate()

CheckingLogin --> GestureLogin : Gesture Login Enabled
CheckingLogin --> MainScreen : Gesture Login Disabled

GestureLogin --> [*] : Navigate to GestureInputActivity
MainScreen --> [*] : Navigate to MainActivity

@enduml
